metadata.name: SagittariusBoy #1
metadata.description: “Sagittarius boy” is the beginning of the journey to the Sagittarius galaxy.You will have your own mounts and weapons.And finally occupy that land and rule the star domain.The SagittariusBoy NFT are minted by consuming RND tokens,Get your own unique appearance atrandom,The style covers sports, punk, war, space leisure and so on.As the mystery of the future is gradually solvedAll the achievements of building the base and exploring the starry sky will belong to every boy,They will also be free to choose their own growth path and ideal place to live.
